{"id": "1171413060473323551", "channel_id": "1171413060473323551", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天米爾拿到了獨家爆料噢！！\n看看你猜對了嗎？今天要介紹的是【血肉界域】！胚胎、心臟、吞噬、融合，哪一個關鍵詞能戳中你呢~\n（據說，血肉界域的喚醒體，都很喜歡以小博大，你會不會是其中一個呢？）\n\n血肉界域天賦 -「猩紅獻祭」\n*回合開始時獲得一定胚胎融合進度，\n   達到100%時將1張「胚胎」置入手牌。\n\n*打出胚胎能夠選擇喚醒體增加狂氣，\n   血肉界域的「狂氣爆發」會消耗胚胎觸發吞噬效果。", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:37:17.419000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😂", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1171413060896968796", "filename": "SPOILER_download_3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1809236, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171413060473323551/1171413060896968796/SPOILER_download_3.png?ex=69fb27ed&is=69f9d66d&hm=5f1c2acfdcdb5c1dae049563286ef34e0286388c1c1b07e48ab4ff072c07a0a4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171413060473323551", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「血肉界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171396762716614717", "channel_id": "1171396762716614717", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家看看這張圖，猜猜這個是什麼呢？\n\nA.碎裂的面具  B.開心和不開心  C.混沌界域  D.我有其他想法", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:32:31.731000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-08T02:31:02.746000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1171396762892771338", "filename": "5f074ef5-96c8-4bc5-a8c8-1500fbc6c701_1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 167757, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171396762716614717/1171396762892771338/5f074ef5-96c8-4bc5-a8c8-1500fbc6c701_1.png?ex=69fb18bf&is=69f9c73f&hm=b1f1ed3bfe9083bdfed29066cc7a930eafa4ade9e5c2a0aead79aa462e902f2b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171396762716614717", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「混沌界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171420057029578812", "channel_id": "1171420057029578812", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "奧吉爾雖然手持著劍，但是他手裡這把是守護之劍。\n騎士是一種無形之物，是忠誠、驍勇與美德賦予了它形體。這把劍也是如此，是守護的意志給予了它劍盾之形。\n\n有趣的是，作為騎士的奧吉爾，竟然也會有想要切磋的心情，你們猜他最想跟誰交流劍術呢？ \n能夠讓奧吉爾也希望切磋劍術的，當然是劍術高超的拉蒙娜啦~", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T12:05:05.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1171420059231584327", "filename": "62ad2134-8e80-427c-ad42-9302cc0d6fd6.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9432807, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171420057029578812/1171420059231584327/62ad2134-8e80-427c-ad42-9302cc0d6fd6.png?ex=69fb2e72&is=69f9dcf2&hm=7f8b236ec3af4c2d35a18f12efe60c0c72500ef8a24bd58dd1785f80e38f639e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171420057029578812", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "騎士「奧吉爾」前來報到！", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171420305005223996", "channel_id": "1171420305005223996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天的新情報來囖~大家知道今天準備預告的喚醒體是什麼武器嗎！\n\nA.雙節棍 B.雙刀 C.雙劍 D.雙錘\n\n誕生於無邊寰宇，戰鬥和破壞是她的本能。\n蘿坦使用的武器當然是霸氣的雙劍啦~\n\n**據說~蘿坦永遠都在追求更宏大更酣暢淋漓的戰鬥，狂熱的戰士的口頭禪一般也比較特別，一起來看看哪些像是她會說的話呢？**\n\nA.認輸吧！勝利是我的囊中之物。\nB.識趣的話，就找個角落乖乖蹲著。\nC.我承認你身上有著強者的氣味，但距離成為我的對手，還差得遠。\nD.討厭的東西啊……果然，還是做事中途放棄的傢伙吧。一想起那種人，昨天的晚餐都要嘔上來了。\nE.認定的對手夭折，這種事我不會讓它發生第二次。\nF.對，就像這樣，用崇拜的眼神仰視我吧。\n\n**確實，都是蘿坦會說的話，不過，也就只有驕傲的蘿坦，能說出這種自信的話了！\n看來大家也很了解蘿坦了，等遊戲正式上線，也要多多體驗這名高傷害戰士哦！**", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T12:06:04.650000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1171420305210753035", "filename": "6f27325651b32449.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 308437, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171420305005223996/1171420305210753035/6f27325651b32449.png?ex=69fb2eac&is=69f9dd2c&hm=2f99aa838d7579400f769b5600cb74062476a2538b2fa3aac567ff9dd2f6f785&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171420305005223996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「蘿坦」的武器很酷哦！", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1171397252682620938", "channel_id": "1171397252682620938", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "當名為「融蝕」的災厄籠罩整個世界\n不僅帶走了人們的性命\n還剝奪了我們銘記他們的權利\n我們必須用盡一切來對抗融蝕\n否則不僅是記憶，連人們最美好的生命也會失去\n而喚醒體是這場戰爭的關鍵\n喚醒體分為4個界域\n【血肉】、【混沌】、【超維】、【深海】\n而連結喚醒體的「Key」是__________，其既是鑰匙也是關鍵！\n\nA.銀鑰    B.各位守密人    C.其他", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:34:28.548000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:34:42.590000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171397252682620938", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「融蝕」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395286598438992"]}
{"id": "1171395702887305216", "channel_id": "1171395702887305216", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "米爾收到了一個新情報！ 快來猜猜看，誰是彌薩格大學是最XX的喚醒體呀？                    \n\nA：理智   B：瘋狂  C：自戀  D：懦弱    E：（你还有其他答案吗？）", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:28:19.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-07T12:07:58.669000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1171395703109591162", "filename": "59cfec98-e882-4045-a743-a64cc618851e.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 799743, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171395702887305216/1171395703109591162/59cfec98-e882-4045-a743-a64cc618851e.png?ex=69fb17c3&is=69f9c643&hm=c7c876e7c2df515c9418e28faffb44857df18a271d879043d7388a348e1b2c17&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171395702887305216", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「朵爾」的小問答", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171412455751176272", "channel_id": "1171412455751176272", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "「深海」界域前來報道！\n其能使用觸腕攻擊敵人\n並且愈戰愈強\n*小貼士：每當敵人死亡時，觸腕傷害也會提升\n而奧瑞塔承載著「深海」界域之力\n也在向各位守密人問好~\n各位守密人猜猜一下哪種行為能夠提高奧瑞塔的好感度呢~\n\nA.帶奧瑞塔去彌薩格大學上課。\nB.每日10點喚醒奧瑞塔。\nC.與奧瑞塔成為夥伴。", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:34:53.242000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1171412458150305792", "filename": "3ad71463-0545-4d79-ac61-4b52854b31ec.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9561182, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171412455751176272/1171412458150305792/3ad71463-0545-4d79-ac61-4b52854b31ec.png?ex=69fb275d&is=69f9d5dd&hm=2258bf311d422db56c8b46118b2abd8183a646f650a8471d19d7bb8ccbdb7d48&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171412455751176272", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海界域「奧瑞塔」喚醒體介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
